premise_source_doc_sentence: The critically successful Solaris features Natalya Bondarchuk  (  Hari  )  , Donatas Banionis  (  Kris Kelvin  )  , Jüri Järvet  (  Dr. Snaut  )  , Vladislav Dvorzhetsky  (  Henri Berton  )  , Nikolai Grinko  (  Kris Kelvin 's Father  )  , Olga Barnet  (  Kris Kelvin 's Mother  )  , Anatoli Solonitsyn  (  Dr. Sartorius  )  , and Sos Sargsyan  (  Dr. Gibarian  )  ; the music is by Johann Sebastian Bach and Eduard Artemyev .
